HEADWORD: Gymnocladus
<hw>Gym*noc"la*dus</hw> <pr>(j⟦icr⟧m*n⟦ocr⟧"l⟦adot⟧*d⟦ucr⟧s)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. Gr. <grk>gymno`s</grk> naked +
